      simp [Subtype.ext_iff, RingHom.map_add]
    map_one' := by
      simp [Subtype.ext_iff, RingHom.map_one]
    map_mul' := by
      intro x y
      simp [Subtype.ext_iff, RingHom.map_mul]
    map_zero' := by
      simp [Subtype.ext_iff, RingHom.map_zero]}
```
